'''Lodog''' is an NPC involved in the quest [[From the Bottom]]. He will give the player {{WynnIcon|prismarine crystals}} Ice Drake Scales in exchange for a {{WynnIcon|redstone lamp}} Golemlus Power Core, obtained from [[Dorroc]].

== Dialogue ==
Before From the Bottom:
* {{Dialogue|green|Lodog|What, you think just cause I'm not one of you Corkians I can't deal in machines- Oh. You...uh. You aren't Corkian, are ya?}}
* {{Dialogue|green|Lodog|Sorry 'bout that. See, a few months ago there was a big party of Corkus idjits that came round, and they had the audacity to insult our forges!}}
* {{Dialogue|green|Lodog|'specially that [[Dr. Legendary|bald-headed, square-faced, gray-haired, legendary SPITSTAIN]]! Oh, I couldn't STAND that guy. So I started dealing in machines, and it's going pretty well I'd say!}}
* {{Dialogue|green|Lodog|...oh, right. Gotta try and pawn some 'a this stuff. I got some rarities in my stock, but mostly I'm lookin' to get some machinery. If ya find any, I'll see what I can offer ya, aight?}}

After From the Bottom:
* {{Dialogue|green|Lodog|This core machine's gonna be a better challenge to figure out than ANY of that smarmy idiot's "[[Lists of mobs/Legendary Island|legendary mechs]]," hah!}}
* {{Dialogue|green|Lodog|...hm? Oh, 's you again! Suppose ya heard me and my little grudge, huh? Yeah. I forget if I told ya this or not, but a few months ago there was a group from [[Corkus]] here.}}
* {{Dialogue|green|Lodog|Hoity-toity lot, they were. Got me into machinery though, even if it was just outta spite. Might not've heard about many Dwarven mages, but they exist!}}
* {{Dialogue|green|Lodog|Electromagic comes nice an' natural to me, so I've started riggin' up these machines. It's kinda funny you brought me somethin' from that [[The Qira Hive (Location)|Hive]], too.}}
* {{Dialogue|green|Lodog|They stopped by here on their way to the Hive, those Corkus idjits. Somethin' about a sponsorship to go see [[Qira]] of all people!}}
* {{Dialogue|green|Lodog|An'! The best part! The idiot came back with a crumpled wrist and this HORRIFIED look- Musta gotten on the Hive witch's bad side!}}
* {{Dialogue|green|Lodog|Heheheh, he got what was comin' to 'im! Serves 'em all right for bein' so high-and-mighty when they ain't even provincially recognized!}}

==Location==
{{Location|location=[[Thanos Bazaar]]|x=33|z=-5126}}

== Trivia ==
* Prior to the [[Version 2.0|2.0 Spellbound Update]], Lodog traded the {{WynnIcon|quartz}} Claw of Lethirath, the Fire Demon in exchange for {{WynnIcon|book}} Bob's Diary.

